  <brief_title>Study of DU-176b Aged 80 Years or Older</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel-group, Multicenter Study of DU-176b in Patients With NVAF Aged 80 Years or Older Who Are Ineligible for Available Oral Anticoagulation Therapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
