  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of edoxaban in patients with
      non-valvular NVAF aged 80 years or older who are ineligible for available oral
      anticoagulation therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
